==German==
===Prefix===
'''Ge-'''

# Forms [[collective noun]]s, almost always [[neuter]] gender. Whenever possible, the root vowel is modified as well: [[Ader]]/[[Geäder]], [[Ast]]/[[Geäst]], [[Berg]]/[[Gebirge]], [[Busch]]/[[Gebüsch]], [[Rippe]]/[[Gerippe]], [[Stein]]/[[Gestein]], [[Strauch]]/[[Gesträuch]], [[Wasser]]/[[Gewässer]], [[Wolke]]/[[Gewölk]].
# With [[verbal noun]]s, it denotes repetition or continuation. All of these nouns are neuter and have no plural. For example: [[ächzen]]/[[Geächze]], [[heulen]]/[[Geheul]], [[reden]]/[[Gerede]], [[seufzen]]/[[Geseufze]].

===Prefix===
'''ge-'''

# Forms [[past participle]]s of verbs: [[essen]]/[[gegessen]], [[haben]]/[[gehabt]], [[sehen]]/[[gesehen]], [[sprechen]]/[[gesprochen]]. Nouns are frequently made from the past participle.

